Transcription.Text: A trinity of figures communes in the hollow of a great saucer. A beacon seen on the shore becomes transfigured into an ominous signal-cum-lookout post. A Corinthian helmet inspires an exploration of hollow form, with the in- scrutable menace of the visor still preserved.
